Environmental Policy	Committing Body	Can you confirm if the environmental commitment or policy has been formally approved or signed by the Board of Directors or a designated representative, indicating their active involvement?
Environmental Policy	Responsibility	Does the environmental management policy clearly identify specific roles responsible for its implementation, such as business unit managers or all employees?
Environmental Policy	Compliance	Does the policy include a statement of commitment to both compliance and proactive measures regarding environmental regulations?
Environmental Policy	Performance	Does the company's policy explicitly state a commitment to improving environmental performance?
Environmental Policy	Targets	Are the environmental targets reported in the policy rather than in an annual or sustainability report?
Environmental Policy	Stakeholder Awareness	What specific measures does the company implement to raise awareness among employees about its environmental management policy and its impacts?
Environmental Policy	Training	Does the company commit to offering training that equips employees with the necessary knowledge to understand and mitigate their work's environmental impacts?
Coverage of Environmental Management Policy	Production and Operations	What qualitative measures are in place to assess the effectiveness of the Environmental Management Policy within the Production and Operations field, and how do these measures contribute to achieving sustainability goals?
Coverage of Environmental Management Policy	Products and Services	What qualitative measures are in place to assess the effectiveness of the Environmental Management Policy in relation to the coverage of products and services, and how do these measures contribute to continuous improvement in environmental performance?
Coverage of Environmental Management Policy	Distribution and Logistics	What qualitative measures are currently in place to assess the effectiveness of the Environmental Management Policy within the Distribution and Logistics subfield, and how do these measures contribute to improving overall policy coverage?
Coverage of Environmental Management Policy	Waste Management	What qualitative measures are in place to assess the effectiveness of the Environmental Management Policy specifically related to waste management, and how do these measures contribute to the overall sustainability goals of the organization?
Coverage of Environmental Management Policy	Suppliers	What qualitative measures are in place to assess the effectiveness of the Environmental Management Policy coverage among suppliers, and how do these measures align with the overall sustainability goals of the organization?
Coverage of Environmental Management Policy	Other Partners	What qualitative measures are in place to assess the effectiveness of the Coverage of Environmental Management Policy among Other Partners, and how do these measures contribute to the overall sustainability goals of the organization?
